Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeGenerator
    Effectively compile the miniRust code to assembly Use of registry : - R0 : Use for calculations, print and all sort of things - R1 : Use for binary operations (along with stack) - R2 : None - R3 : None - R4 : Use for saving sign of int to print - R5 : Mode for printing (0 : int, 1 : boolean, 2 : String, 3 : CRLF) - R6 : Use as temporary registry for printing - R7 : Contains a copy of current value while printing
    MiniRustCompiler
    Implement a compiler for MiniRust Language.
    Scope
    Correspond to a Scope in code (Function, block, loop ...).
    A scope contains following informations : An ancestor An origin A name An offset, corresponding to current offset An "innerScopeList", corresponding to a list of scope of anonymous block inside this scope A table, containing every variables, parameters A second table, containing scope of non-anonymous block
    TDS
    Implement a Symbol table by associating a scope to each block and var/function to each scope.
    Type
    Implement a type.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SemanticException
    Exception thrown when a semantic control fails.
